                            <comment id="17882827" author="JIRAUSER305622" created="Thu, 19 Sep 2024 00:00:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=epugh&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;epugh&quot;&gt;epugh&lt;/a&gt; I&apos;ve also created a backport PR against branch_9_7 in case there will be a patch release for 9.7 in the future.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17884256" author="jira-bot" created="Tue, 24 Sep 2024 12:23:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 6d380dbee31bc64809d2374bd0f81ccfe807a073 in solr&apos;s branch refs/heads/main from Eric Pugh&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://gitbox.apache.org/repos/asf?p=solr.git;h=6d380dbee31&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://gitbox.apache.org/repos/asf?p=solr.git;h=6d380dbee31&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Scavange one change from the &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-17457&quot; title=&quot;StatusTool does not support --max-wait-secs&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-17457&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-17457&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; bug fix (#2718)&lt;/p&gt;
</comment>
